column5: Quiet and secluded, the Guest House is located on a beautiful waterfront gated Estate with 4+ acres of land on Lake Travis. Owners built the Guest House with all modern conveniences in 2015.   Guest have access to the water and can tie up their boat/jet ski to owners private dock.  There are restaurants and lots of things to do within minutes of the property.
column8: Lake Travis Waterfront House Within Gated Estate
